Test – Configured Media Module Directory


---

✅ Description

The Media module has been configured to store uploaded media files in a dedicated directory structure.
Testing is required to ensure that:

Media uploads follow the configured directory path,

Files are stored in the correct folder structure,

Existing media is not affected,

Media references on pages continue to work.



---

✅ Acceptance Criteria (GIVEN / WHEN / THEN)

Given the media module directory configuration is updated,
When a user uploads new media files from the backend,
Then the files should be stored in the correct configured directory structure and should be accessible without breaking any media references on the site.

